alias Sensor d0 alias memoriaV d2 alias memoriaH d3 alias vertical r0 alias horizontal r1 alias hasSun r2 alias men r3 loop: l hasSun Sensor Activate
j main
main: l vertical Sensor Vertical l horizontal Sensor Horizontal
sub vertical 90 vertical #sub horizontal horizontal 90 s memoriaH Setting horizontal s memoriaV Setting vertical j main

alias Battery d0 alias Generator d1
alias ratio r0
define minRatio 0.5 define maxRatio 0.8
discharging: s Generator On 0 sleep 1 l ratio Battery Ratio blt ratio minRatio charging j discharging
charging: s Generator On 1 sleep 1 l ratio Battery Ratio bgt ratio maxRatio discharging j charging

alias Battery d0 alias Generator d1

define minRatio 0.5 define maxRatio 0.9

charging: s Generator On 1 sleep 1 l ratio Battery Ratio bgt ratio maxRatio discharging j charging
